            <title>[PIG-4037] TestHBaseStorage, TestAccumuloPigCluster has failures with hadoopversion=23</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4037</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4005&quot; title=&quot;depend on hbase-hadoop2-compat rather than hbase-hadoop1-compat when hbaseversion is 95&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4005&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-4005&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; enabled TestHBaseStorage to be run with hadoopversion=23, but there are 5 test failures and 1 error. TestAccumuloPigCluster fail for the same reason.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
